Module gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core

Package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.xml

package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.xml
Support for loading Metaschema information from an XML-based Metaschema module.

Provides an implementation of the Metaschema model (gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model) using an underlying XML format.
